54int32_t __weak lsm6dso32_read_reg(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, uint8_t reg,
55 uint8_t *data,
56 uint16_t len)
57{
58 int32_t ret;
59
60 ret = ctx->read_reg(ctx->handle, reg, data, len);
61
62 return ret;
63}

97float_t lsm6dso32_from_fs4_to_mg(int16_t lsb)

172int32_t lsm6dso32_xl_full_scale_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
173 lsm6dso32_fs_xl_t val)
174{
175 lsm6dso32_ctrl1_xl_t ctrl1_xl;
176 int32_t ret;
177
178 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_CTRL1_XL,
179 (uint8_t *)&ctrl1_xl, 1);
180
181 if (ret == 0)
182 {
183 ctrl1_xl.fs_xl = (uint8_t) val & 0x03U;
184 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_CTRL1_XL,
185 (uint8_t *)&ctrl1_xl, 1);
186 }
187
188 return ret;
189}
190
199int32_t lsm6dso32_xl_full_scale_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
200 lsm6dso32_fs_xl_t *val)
201{
202 lsm6dso32_ctrl1_xl_t reg;
203 int32_t ret;
204
205 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_CTRL1_XL, (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
206
207 switch (reg.fs_xl)
208 {
209 case LSM6DSO32_4g:
210 *val = LSM6DSO32_4g;
211 break;
212
213 case LSM6DSO32_8g:
214 *val = LSM6DSO32_8g;
215 break;
216
217 case LSM6DSO32_16g:
218 *val = LSM6DSO32_16g;
219 break;
220
221 case LSM6DSO32_32g:
222 *val = LSM6DSO32_32g;
223 break;
224
225 default:
226 *val = LSM6DSO32_4g;
227 break;
228 }
229
230 return ret;
231}

242int32_t lsm6dso32_xl_data_rate_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
243 lsm6dso32_odr_xl_t val)
244{
245 lsm6dso32_ctrl1_xl_t ctrl1_xl;
246 lsm6dso32_ctrl5_c_t ctrl5_c;
247 lsm6dso32_ctrl6_c_t ctrl6_c;
248 lsm6dso32_func_cfg_access_t func_cfg_access;
249 int32_t ret;
250
251 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_CTRL1_XL,
252 (uint8_t *)&ctrl1_xl, 1);
253
254 if (ret == 0)
255 {
256 ctrl1_xl.odr_xl = (uint8_t) LSM6DSO32_XL_ODR_OFF & 0x0FU;
257 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_CTRL1_XL,
258 (uint8_t *)&ctrl1_xl, 1);
259 }
260
261 if (ret == 0)
262 {
263 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FUNC_CFG_ACCESS,
264 (uint8_t *)&func_cfg_access, 1);
265 }
266
267 if (ret == 0)
268 {
269 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_CTRL5_C, (uint8_t *) &ctrl5_c, 1);
270 }
271
272 if (ret == 0)
273 {
274 ctrl5_c.xl_ulp_en = ((uint8_t)val & 0x20U) >> 5;
275 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_CTRL5_C,
276 (uint8_t *) &ctrl5_c, 1);
277 }
278
279 if (ret == 0)
280 {
281 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_CTRL6_C, (uint8_t *) &ctrl6_c, 1);
282 }
283
284 if (ret == 0)
285 {
286 ctrl6_c.xl_hm_mode = ((uint8_t)val & 0x10U) >> 4;
287 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_CTRL6_C,
288 (uint8_t *) &ctrl6_c, 1);
289 }
290
291 if (ret == 0)
292 {
293 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_CTRL1_XL,
294 (uint8_t *)&ctrl1_xl, 1);
295 }
296
297 if (ret == 0)
298 {
299 ctrl1_xl.odr_xl = (uint8_t) val & 0x0FU;
300 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_CTRL1_XL,
301 (uint8_t *)&ctrl1_xl, 1);
302 }
303
304 return ret;
305}

316int32_t lsm6dso32_xl_data_rate_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
317 lsm6dso32_odr_xl_t *val)
318{
319 lsm6dso32_ctrl1_xl_t ctrl1_xl;
320 lsm6dso32_ctrl5_c_t ctrl5_c;
321 lsm6dso32_ctrl6_c_t ctrl6_c;
322 lsm6dso32_func_cfg_access_t func_cfg_access;
323 int32_t ret;
324
325 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_CTRL1_XL,
326 (uint8_t *)&ctrl1_xl, 1);
327
328 if (ret == 0)
329 {
330 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FUNC_CFG_ACCESS,
331 (uint8_t *)&func_cfg_access, 1);
332 }
333
334 if (ret == 0)
335 {

526int32_t lsm6dso32_gy_data_rate_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
527 lsm6dso32_odr_g_t val)
528{
529 lsm6dso32_ctrl2_g_t ctrl2_g;
530 lsm6dso32_ctrl7_g_t ctrl7_g;
531 int32_t ret;
532
533 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_CTRL2_G, (uint8_t *)&ctrl2_g, 1);
534
535 if (ret == 0)
536 {
537 ctrl2_g.odr_g = (uint8_t) LSM6DSO32_GY_ODR_OFF & 0x0FU;
538 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_CTRL2_G, (uint8_t *)&ctrl2_g, 1);
539 }
540
541 if (ret == 0)
542 {
543 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_CTRL7_G, (uint8_t *)&ctrl7_g, 1);
544 }
545
546 if (ret == 0)
547 {
548 ctrl7_g.g_hm_mode = ((uint8_t)val & 0x10U) >> 4;
549 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_CTRL7_G, (uint8_t *)&ctrl7_g, 1);
550 }
551
552 if (ret == 0)
553 {
554 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_CTRL2_G, (uint8_t *)&ctrl2_g, 1);
555 }
556
557 if (ret == 0)
558 {
559 ctrl2_g.odr_g = (uint8_t)val & 0x0FU;
560 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_CTRL2_G, (uint8_t *)&ctrl2_g, 1);
561 }
562
563 return ret;
564}

670int32_t lsm6dso32_block_data_update_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
671 uint8_t val)
672{
673 lsm6dso32_ctrl3_c_t reg;
674 int32_t ret;
675
676 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_CTRL3_C, (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
677
678 if (ret == 0)
679 {
680 reg.bdu = val;
681 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_CTRL3_C, (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
682 }
683
684 return ret;
685}

778int32_t lsm6dso32_all_sources_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
779 lsm6dso32_all_sources_t *val)
780{
781 int32_t ret;
782
783 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_ALL_INT_SRC,
784 (uint8_t *)&val->all_int_src, 1);
785
786 if (ret == 0)
787 {
788 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_WAKE_UP_SRC,
789 (uint8_t *)&val->wake_up_src, 1);
790 }
791
792 if (ret == 0)
793 {
794 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_TAP_SRC,
795 (uint8_t *)&val->tap_src, 1);
796 }
797
798 if (ret == 0)
799 {
800 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_D6D_SRC,
801 (uint8_t *)&val->d6d_src, 1);
802 }
803
804 if (ret == 0)
805 {
806 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_STATUS_REG,
807 (uint8_t *)&val->status_reg, 1);
808 }
809
810 if (ret == 0)
811 {
812 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
813 }
814
815 if (ret == 0)
816 {
817 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMB_FUNC_STATUS,
818 (uint8_t *)&val->emb_func_status, 1);
819 }
820
821 if (ret == 0)
822 {
823 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FSM_STATUS_A,
824 (uint8_t *)&val->fsm_status_a, 1);
825 }
826
827 if (ret == 0)
828 {
829 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FSM_STATUS_B,
830 (uint8_t *)&val->fsm_status_b, 1);
831 }
832
833 if (ret == 0)
834 {
835 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_USER_BANK);
836 }
837
838 return ret;
839}

1208int32_t lsm6dso32_rounding_mode_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
1209 lsm6dso32_rounding_t *val)
1210{
1211 lsm6dso32_ctrl5_c_t reg;
1212 int32_t ret;
1213
1214 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_CTRL5_C, (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
1215
1216 switch (reg.rounding)
1217 {
1218 case LSM6DSO32_NO_ROUND:
1219 *val = LSM6DSO32_NO_ROUND;
1220 break;
1221
1222 case LSM6DSO32_ROUND_XL:
1223 *val = LSM6DSO32_ROUND_XL;
1224 break;
1225
1226 case LSM6DSO32_ROUND_GY:
1227 *val = LSM6DSO32_ROUND_GY;
1228 break;
1229
1230 case LSM6DSO32_ROUND_GY_XL:
1231 *val = LSM6DSO32_ROUND_GY_XL;
1232 break;
1233
1234 default:
1235 *val = LSM6DSO32_NO_ROUND;
1236 break;
1237 }
1238
1239 return ret;
1240}

1371int32_t lsm6dso32_steps_reset(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx)
1372{
1373 lsm6dso32_emb_func_src_t reg;
1374 int32_t ret;
1375
1376 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
1377
1378 if (ret == 0)
1379 {
1380 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMB_FUNC_SRC, (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
1381 }
1382
1383 if (ret == 0)
1384 {
1385 reg.pedo_rst_step = PROPERTY_ENABLE;
1386 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMB_FUNC_SRC,
1387 (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
1388 }
1389
1390 if (ret == 0)
1391 {
1392 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_USER_BANK);
1393 }
1394
1395 return ret;
1396}

1479 (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
1480

1482 {
1483 reg.reg_access = (uint8_t)val;

1490
1500int32_t lsm6dso32_mem_bank_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
1501 lsm6dso32_reg_access_t *val)
1502{
1503 lsm6dso32_func_cfg_access_t reg;
1504 int32_t ret;
1505
1506 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FUNC_CFG_ACCESS,
1507 (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
1508
1509 switch (reg.reg_access)
1510 {
1511 case LSM6DSO32_USER_BANK:
1512 *val = LSM6DSO32_USER_BANK;
1513 break;
1514
1515 case LSM6DSO32_SENSOR_HUB_BANK:
1516 *val = LSM6DSO32_SENSOR_HUB_BANK;
1517 break;
1518
1519 case LSM6DSO32_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK:
1520 *val = LSM6DSO32_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK;
1521 break;
1522
1523 default:
1524 *val = LSM6DSO32_USER_BANK;
1525 break;
1526 }
1527
1528 return ret;
1529}
1530
1540int32_t lsm6dso32_ln_pg_write_byte(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
1541 uint16_t address,
1542 uint8_t *val)
1543{
1544 lsm6dso32_page_rw_t page_rw;
1545 lsm6dso32_page_sel_t page_sel;
1546 lsm6dso32_page_address_t page_address;
1547 int32_t ret;
1548
1549 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
1550
1551 if (ret == 0)
1552 {
1553 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
1554 }
1555
1556 if (ret == 0)
1557 {
1558 page_rw.page_rw = 0x02; /* page_write enable */
1559 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_RW,
1560 (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
1561 }
1562
1563 if (ret == 0)
1564 {
1565 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_SEL,
1566 (uint8_t *) &page_sel, 1);
1567 }
1568
1569 if (ret == 0)
1570 {
1571 page_sel.page_sel = ((uint8_t)(address >> 8) & 0x0FU);
1572 page_sel.not_used_01 = 1;
1573 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_SEL,
1574 (uint8_t *) &page_sel, 1);
1575 }
1576
1577 if (ret == 0)
1578 {
1579 page_address.page_addr = (uint8_t)address & 0xFFU;
1580 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_ADDRESS,
1581 (uint8_t *)&page_address, 1);
1582 }
1583
1584 if (ret == 0)
1585 {
1586 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_VALUE, val, 1);
1587 }
1588
1589 if (ret == 0)
1590 {
1591 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
1592 }
1593
1594 if (ret == 0)
1595 {
1596 page_rw.page_rw = 0x00; /* page_write disable */
1597 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_RW,
1598 (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
1599 }
1600
1601 if (ret == 0)
1602 {
1603 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_USER_BANK);
1604 }
1605
1606 return ret;
1607}
1608
1619int32_t lsm6dso32_ln_pg_write(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, uint16_t address,
1620 uint8_t *buf, uint8_t len)
1621{
1622 lsm6dso32_page_rw_t page_rw;
1623 lsm6dso32_page_sel_t page_sel;
1624 lsm6dso32_page_address_t page_address;
1625 int32_t ret;
1626
1627 uint8_t msb, lsb;
1628 uint8_t i ;
1629 msb = ((uint8_t)(address >> 8) & 0x0FU);
1630 lsb = (uint8_t)address & 0xFFU;
1631 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
1632
1633 if (ret == 0)
1634 {
1635 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
1636 }
1637
1638 if (ret == 0)
1639 {
1640 page_rw.page_rw = 0x02; /* page_write enable*/
1641 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_RW,
1642 (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
1643 }
1644
1645 if (ret == 0)
1646 {
1647 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_SEL,
1648 (uint8_t *) &page_sel, 1);
1649 }
1650
1651 if (ret == 0)
1652 {
1653 page_sel.page_sel = msb;
1654 page_sel.not_used_01 = 1;
1655 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_SEL,
1656 (uint8_t *) &page_sel, 1);
1657 }
1658
1659 if (ret == 0)
1660 {
1661 page_address.page_addr = lsb;
1662 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_ADDRESS,
1663 (uint8_t *)&page_address, 1);
1664 }
1665
1666 if (ret == 0)
1667 {
1668 for (i = 0; ((i < len) && (ret == 0)); i++)
1669 {
1670 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_VALUE, &buf[i], 1);
1671
1672 /* Check if page wrap */
1673 if ((lsb == 0x00U) && (ret == 0))
1674 {
1675 lsb++;
1676 msb++;
1677 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_SEL,
1678 (uint8_t *)&page_sel, 1);
1679
1680 if (ret == 0)
1681 {
1682 page_sel.page_sel = msb;
1683 page_sel.not_used_01 = 1;
1684 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_SEL,
1685 (uint8_t *)&page_sel, 1);
1686 }
1687 }
1688 }
1689
1690 page_sel.page_sel = 0;
1691 page_sel.not_used_01 = 1;
1692 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_SEL,
1693 (uint8_t *) &page_sel, 1);
1694 }
1695
1696 if (ret == 0)
1697 {
1698 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
1699 }
1700
1701 if (ret == 0)
1702 {
1703 page_rw.page_rw = 0x00; /* page_write disable */
1704 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_RW,
1705 (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
1706 }
1707
1708 if (ret == 0)
1709 {
1710 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_USER_BANK);
1711 }
1712
1713 return ret;
1714}
1715
1725int32_t lsm6dso32_ln_pg_read_byte(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, uint16_t address,
1726 uint8_t *val)
1727{
1728 lsm6dso32_page_rw_t page_rw;
1729 lsm6dso32_page_sel_t page_sel;
1730 lsm6dso32_page_address_t page_address;
1731 int32_t ret;
1732
1733 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
1734
1735 if (ret == 0)
1736 {
1737 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
1738 }
1739
1740 if (ret == 0)
1741 {
1742 page_rw.page_rw = 0x01; /* page_read enable*/
1743 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_RW,
1744 (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
1745 }
1746
1747 if (ret == 0)
1748 {
1749 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_SEL,
1750 (uint8_t *) &page_sel, 1);
1751 }
1752
1753 if (ret == 0)
1754 {
1755 page_sel.page_sel = ((uint8_t)(address >> 8) & 0x0FU);
1756 page_sel.not_used_01 = 1;
1757 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_SEL,
1758 (uint8_t *) &page_sel, 1);
1759 }
1760
1761 if (ret == 0)
1762 {
1763 page_address.page_addr = (uint8_t)address & 0x00FFU;
1764 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_ADDRESS,
1765 (uint8_t *)&page_address, 1);
1766 }
1767
1768 if (ret == 0)
1769 {
1770 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_VALUE, val, 2);
1771 }
1772
1773 if (ret == 0)
1774 {
1775 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
1776 }
1777
1778 if (ret == 0)
1779 {
1780 page_rw.page_rw = 0x00; /* page_read disable */
1781 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_RW,
1782 (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
1783 }
1784
1785 if (ret == 0)
1786 {
1787 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_USER_BANK);
1788 }
1789
1790 return ret;
1791}
1792

2617int32_t lsm6dso32_xl_hp_path_internal_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
2618 lsm6dso32_slope_fds_t val)
2619{
2620 lsm6dso32_tap_cfg0_t reg;
2621 int32_t ret;
2622
2623 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_TAP_CFG0, (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
2624

3375 (uint8_t *)&val->md2_cfg, 1);
3376 }
3377
3378 if (ret == 0)
3379 {
3380 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_TAP_CFG2,
3381 (uint8_t *) &tap_cfg2, 1);
3382 }
3383
3384 if (ret == 0)
3385 {
3386 ret = lsm6dso32_pin_int1_route_get(ctx, &pin_int1_route);
3387 }
3388
3389 if (ret == 0)
3390 {
3391 if ((val->int2_ctrl.int2_cnt_bdr
3392 | val->int2_ctrl.int2_drdy_g
3393 | val->int2_ctrl.int2_drdy_temp
3394 | val->int2_ctrl.int2_drdy_xl
3395 | val->int2_ctrl.int2_fifo_full
3396 | val->int2_ctrl.int2_fifo_ovr
3397 | val->int2_ctrl.int2_fifo_th
3398 | val->md2_cfg.int2_6d
3399 | val->md2_cfg.int2_double_tap
3400 | val->md2_cfg.int2_ff
3401 | val->md2_cfg.int2_wu
3402 | val->md2_cfg.int2_single_tap
3403 | val->md2_cfg.int2_sleep_change
3404 | pin_int1_route.int1_ctrl.den_drdy_flag
3405 | pin_int1_route.int1_ctrl.int1_boot
3406 | pin_int1_route.int1_ctrl.int1_cnt_bdr
3407 | pin_int1_route.int1_ctrl.int1_drdy_g
3408 | pin_int1_route.int1_ctrl.int1_drdy_xl
3409 | pin_int1_route.int1_ctrl.int1_fifo_full
3410 | pin_int1_route.int1_ctrl.int1_fifo_ovr
3411 | pin_int1_route.int1_ctrl.int1_fifo_th
3412 | pin_int1_route.md1_cfg.int1_6d
3413 | pin_int1_route.md1_cfg.int1_double_tap
3414 | pin_int1_route.md1_cfg.int1_ff
3415 | pin_int1_route.md1_cfg.int1_wu
3416 | pin_int1_route.md1_cfg.int1_single_tap
3417 | pin_int1_route.md1_cfg.int1_sleep_change) != PROPERTY_DISABLE)
3418 {
3419 tap_cfg2.interrupts_enable = PROPERTY_ENABLE;
3420 }
3421
3422 else
3423 {
3424 tap_cfg2.interrupts_enable = PROPERTY_DISABLE;
3425 }
3426
3427 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_TAP_CFG2,
3428 (uint8_t *) &tap_cfg2, 1);
3429 }
3430
3431 return ret;
3432}
3433
3443int32_t lsm6dso32_pin_int2_route_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
3444 lsm6dso32_pin_int2_route_t *val)
3445{
3446 int32_t ret;
3447
3448 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
3449
3450 if (ret == 0)
3451 {
3452 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMB_FUNC_INT2,
3453 (uint8_t *)&val->emb_func_int2, 1);
3454 }
3455
3456 if (ret == 0)
3457 {
3458 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FSM_INT2_A,
3459 (uint8_t *)&val->fsm_int2_a, 1);
3460 }
3461
3462 if (ret == 0)
3463 {
3464 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FSM_INT2_B,
3465 (uint8_t *)&val->fsm_int2_b, 1);
3466 }
3467
3468 if (ret == 0)
3469 {
3470 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_USER_BANK);
3471 }
3472
3473 if (ret == 0)
3474 {
3475 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_INT2_CTRL,
3476 (uint8_t *)&val->int2_ctrl, 1);
3477 }
3478
3479 if (ret == 0)
3480 {
3481 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_MD2_CFG,
3482 (uint8_t *)&val->md2_cfg, 1);
3483 }
3484
3485 return ret;
3486}

3657int32_t lsm6dso32_int_notification_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
3658 lsm6dso32_lir_t val)
3659{
3660 lsm6dso32_tap_cfg0_t tap_cfg0;
3661 lsm6dso32_page_rw_t page_rw;
3662 int32_t ret;
3663
3664 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_TAP_CFG0,
3665 (uint8_t *) &tap_cfg0, 1);
3666
3667 if (ret == 0)
3668 {
3669 tap_cfg0.lir = (uint8_t)val & 0x01U;
3670 tap_cfg0.int_clr_on_read = (uint8_t)val & 0x01U;
3671 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_TAP_CFG0,
3672 (uint8_t *) &tap_cfg0, 1);
3673 }
3674
3675 if (ret == 0)
3676 {
3677 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
3678 }
3679
3680 if (ret == 0)
3681 {
3682 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
3683 }
3684
3685 if (ret == 0)
3686 {
3687 page_rw.emb_func_lir = ((uint8_t)val & 0x02U) >> 1;
3688 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_RW,
3689 (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
3690 }
3691
3692 if (ret == 0)
3693 {
3694 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_USER_BANK);
3695 }
3696
3697 return ret;
3698}
3699
3708int32_t lsm6dso32_int_notification_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
3709 lsm6dso32_lir_t *val)
3710{
3711 lsm6dso32_tap_cfg0_t tap_cfg0;
3712 lsm6dso32_page_rw_t page_rw;
3713 int32_t ret;
3714
3715 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_TAP_CFG0,
3716 (uint8_t *) &tap_cfg0, 1);
3717
3718 if (ret == 0)
3719 {
3720 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
3721 }
3722
3723 if (ret == 0)
3724 {
3725 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
3726 }
3727
3728 if (ret == 0)
3729 {
3730 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_USER_BANK);
3731 }
3732
3733 if (ret == 0)
3734 {
3735 switch ((page_rw.emb_func_lir << 1) | tap_cfg0.lir)
3736 {
3737 case LSM6DSO32_ALL_INT_PULSED:
3738 *val = LSM6DSO32_ALL_INT_PULSED;
3739 break;
3740
3741 case LSM6DSO32_BASE_LATCHED_EMB_PULSED:
3742 *val = LSM6DSO32_BASE_LATCHED_EMB_PULSED;
3743 break;
3744
3745 case LSM6DSO32_BASE_PULSED_EMB_LATCHED:
3746 *val = LSM6DSO32_BASE_PULSED_EMB_LATCHED;
3747 break;
3748
3749 case LSM6DSO32_ALL_INT_LATCHED:
3750 *val = LSM6DSO32_ALL_INT_LATCHED;
3751 break;
3752
3753 default:
3754 *val = LSM6DSO32_ALL_INT_PULSED;
3755 break;
3756 }
3757
3758 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
3759 }
3760
3761 if (ret == 0)
3762 {
3763 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t *) &page_rw, 1);
3764 }
3765
3766 if (ret == 0)
3767 {
3768 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_USER_BANK);
3769 }
3770
3771 return ret;
3772}

4992
5002int32_t lsm6dso32_ff_dur_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, uint8_t val)
5003{
5004 lsm6dso32_wake_up_dur_t wake_up_dur;
5005 lsm6dso32_free_fall_t free_fall;
5006 int32_t ret;
5007
5008 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_WAKE_UP_DUR,
5009 (uint8_t *)&wake_up_dur, 1);
5010
5011 if (ret == 0)
5012 {
5013 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FREE_FALL,
5014 (uint8_t *)&free_fall, 1);
5015 }
5016
5017 if (ret == 0)
5018 {
5019 wake_up_dur.ff_dur = ((uint8_t)val & 0x20U) >> 5;
5020 free_fall.ff_dur = (uint8_t)val & 0x1FU;
5021 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_WAKE_UP_DUR,
5022 (uint8_t *)&wake_up_dur, 1);
5023 }
5024
5025 if (ret == 0)
5026 {
5027 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FREE_FALL,
5028 (uint8_t *)&free_fall, 1);
5029 }
5030
5031 return ret;
5032}
5033
5043int32_t lsm6dso32_ff_dur_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, uint8_t *val)
5044{
5045 lsm6dso32_wake_up_dur_t wake_up_dur;
5046 lsm6dso32_free_fall_t free_fall;
5047 int32_t ret;
5048
5049 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_WAKE_UP_DUR,
5050 (uint8_t *)&wake_up_dur, 1);
5051
5052 if (ret == 0)
5053 {
5054 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FREE_FALL,
5055 (uint8_t *)&free_fall, 1);
5056 *val = (wake_up_dur.ff_dur << 5) + free_fall.ff_dur;
5057 }
5058
5059 return ret;
5060}
5061
5083int32_t lsm6dso32_fifo_watermark_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, uint16_t val)
5084{
5085 lsm6dso32_fifo_ctrl1_t fifo_ctrl1;
5086 lsm6dso32_fifo_ctrl2_t fifo_ctrl2;
5087 int32_t ret;
5088
5089 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FIFO_CTRL2,
5090 (uint8_t *)&fifo_ctrl2, 1);
5091
5092 if (ret == 0)
5093 {
5094 fifo_ctrl1.wtm = 0x00FFU & (uint8_t)val;
5095 fifo_ctrl2.wtm = (uint8_t)((0x0100U & val) >> 8);
5096 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FIFO_CTRL1,
5097 (uint8_t *)&fifo_ctrl1, 1);
5098 }
5099
5100 if (ret == 0)
5101 {
5102 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FIFO_CTRL2,
5103 (uint8_t *)&fifo_ctrl2, 1);
5104 }
5105
5106 return ret;
5107}
5108
5117int32_t lsm6dso32_fifo_watermark_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, uint16_t *val)
5118{
5119 lsm6dso32_fifo_ctrl1_t fifo_ctrl1;
5120 lsm6dso32_fifo_ctrl2_t fifo_ctrl2;
5121 int32_t ret;
5122
5123 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FIFO_CTRL1,
5124 (uint8_t *)&fifo_ctrl1, 1);
5125
5126 if (ret == 0)
5127 {
5128 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FIFO_CTRL2,
5129 (uint8_t *)&fifo_ctrl2, 1);
5130 *val = ((uint16_t)fifo_ctrl2.wtm << 8) + (uint16_t)fifo_ctrl1.wtm;
5131 }
5132
5133 return ret;
5134}

5145int32_t lsm6dso32_compression_algo_init_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,

5147{
5148 lsm6dso32_emb_func_init_b_t reg;

5150

5152
5153 if (ret == 0)
5154 {
5155 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMB_FUNC_INIT_B,
5156 (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
5157 }
5158
5159 if (ret == 0)
5160 {
5161 reg.fifo_compr_init = val;

5163 (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
5164 }

5172}
5173
5183int32_t lsm6dso32_compression_algo_init_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
5184 uint8_t *val)
5185{
5186 lsm6dso32_emb_func_init_b_t reg;
5187 int32_t ret;
5188
5189 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
5190
5191 if (ret == 0)
5192 {
5193 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMB_FUNC_INIT_B,
5194 (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
5195 }
5196
5197 if (ret == 0)
5198 {
5199 *val = reg.fifo_compr_init;
5200 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_USER_BANK);
5201 }
5202
5203 return ret;
5204}
5205
5215int32_t lsm6dso32_compression_algo_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
5216 lsm6dso32_uncoptr_rate_t val)
5217{
5218 lsm6dso32_emb_func_en_b_t emb_func_en_b;
5219 lsm6dso32_fifo_ctrl2_t fifo_ctrl2;
5220 int32_t ret;
5221
5222 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
5223
5224 if (ret == 0)
5225 {
5226 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMB_FUNC_EN_B,
5227 (uint8_t *)&emb_func_en_b, 1);
5228 }
5229
5230 if (ret == 0)
5231 {
5232 emb_func_en_b.fifo_compr_en = ((uint8_t)val & 0x04U) >> 2;
5233 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMB_FUNC_EN_B,
5234 (uint8_t *)&emb_func_en_b, 1);
5235 }
5236
5237 if (ret == 0)
5238 {
5239 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_USER_BANK);
5240 }
5241
5242 if (ret == 0)
5243 {
5244 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FIFO_CTRL2,
5245 (uint8_t *)&fifo_ctrl2, 1);
5246 }
5247
5248 if (ret == 0)
5249 {
5250 fifo_ctrl2.fifo_compr_rt_en = ((uint8_t)val & 0x04U) >> 2;
5251 fifo_ctrl2.uncoptr_rate = (uint8_t)val & 0x03U;
5252 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FIFO_CTRL2,
5253 (uint8_t *)&fifo_ctrl2, 1);
5254 }
5255
5256 return ret;
5257}
5258
5268int32_t lsm6dso32_compression_algo_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
5269 lsm6dso32_uncoptr_rate_t *val)
5270{
5271 lsm6dso32_fifo_ctrl2_t reg;
5272 int32_t ret;
5273
5274 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FIFO_CTRL2, (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
5275
5276 switch ((reg.fifo_compr_rt_en << 2) | reg.uncoptr_rate)
5277 {
5278 case LSM6DSO32_CMP_DISABLE:
5279 *val = LSM6DSO32_CMP_DISABLE;
5280 break;
5281
5282 case LSM6DSO32_CMP_ALWAYS:
5283 *val = LSM6DSO32_CMP_ALWAYS;
5284 break;
5285
5286 case LSM6DSO32_CMP_8_TO_1:
5287 *val = LSM6DSO32_CMP_8_TO_1;
5288 break;
5289
5290 case LSM6DSO32_CMP_16_TO_1:
5291 *val = LSM6DSO32_CMP_16_TO_1;
5292 break;
5293
5294 case LSM6DSO32_CMP_32_TO_1:
5295 *val = LSM6DSO32_CMP_32_TO_1;
5296 break;
5297
5298 default:
5299 *val = LSM6DSO32_CMP_DISABLE;
5300 break;
5301 }
5302
5303 return ret;
5304}

5987int32_t lsm6dso32_batch_counter_threshold_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
5988 uint16_t val)
5989{
5990 lsm6dso32_counter_bdr_reg1_t counter_bdr_reg1;

5992 int32_t ret;
5993

5995 (uint8_t *)&counter_bdr_reg1, 1);
5996
5997 if (ret == 0)
5998 {
5999 counter_bdr_reg2.cnt_bdr_th = 0x00FFU & (uint8_t)val;
6000 counter_bdr_reg1.cnt_bdr_th = (uint8_t)(0x0700U & val) >> 8;
6001 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_COUNTER_BDR_REG1,
6002 (uint8_t *)&counter_bdr_reg1, 1);
6003 }
6004
6005 if (ret == 0)
6006 {
6007 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_COUNTER_BDR_REG2,
6008 (uint8_t *)&counter_bdr_reg2, 1);
6009 }
6010
6011 return ret;
6012}
6013
6023int32_t lsm6dso32_batch_counter_threshold_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
6024 uint16_t *val)
6025{
6026 lsm6dso32_counter_bdr_reg1_t counter_bdr_reg1;
6027 lsm6dso32_counter_bdr_reg2_t counter_bdr_reg2;
6028 int32_t ret;
6029
6030 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_COUNTER_BDR_REG1,
6031 (uint8_t *)&counter_bdr_reg1, 1);
6032
6033 if (ret == 0)
6034 {
6035 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_COUNTER_BDR_REG2,
6036 (uint8_t *)&counter_bdr_reg2, 1);
6037 *val = ((uint16_t)counter_bdr_reg1.cnt_bdr_th << 8)
6038 + (uint16_t)counter_bdr_reg2.cnt_bdr_th;
6039 }
6040
6041 return ret;
6042}

6920
6942int32_t lsm6dso32_pedo_sens_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
6943 lsm6dso32_pedo_md_t val)
6944{
6945 lsm6dso32_emb_func_en_a_t emb_func_en_a;
6946 lsm6dso32_emb_func_en_b_t emb_func_en_b;
6947 lsm6dso32_pedo_cmd_reg_t pedo_cmd_reg;
6948 int32_t ret;
6949
6950 ret = lsm6dso32_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PEDO_CMD_REG,
6951 (uint8_t *)&pedo_cmd_reg);
6952
6953 if (ret == 0)
6954 {
6955 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
6956 }
6957
6958 if (ret == 0)
6959 {
6960 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMB_FUNC_EN_A,
6961 (uint8_t *)&emb_func_en_a, 1);
6962 }
6963
6964 if (ret == 0)
6965 {
6966 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMB_FUNC_EN_B,
6967 (uint8_t *)&emb_func_en_b, 1);
6968 emb_func_en_a.pedo_en = (uint8_t)val & 0x01U;
6969 emb_func_en_b.pedo_adv_en = ((uint8_t)val & 0x02U) >> 1;
6970 pedo_cmd_reg.fp_rejection_en = ((uint8_t)val & 0x10U) >> 4;
6971 pedo_cmd_reg.ad_det_en = ((uint8_t)val & 0x20U) >> 5;
6972 }
6973
6974 if (ret == 0)
6975 {
6976 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMB_FUNC_EN_A,
6977 (uint8_t *)&emb_func_en_a, 1);
6978 }
6979
6980 if (ret == 0)
6981 {
6982 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMB_FUNC_EN_B,
6983 (uint8_t *)&emb_func_en_b, 1);
6984 }
6985
6986 if (ret == 0)
6987 {
6988 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_USER_BANK);
6989 }
6990
6991 if (ret == 0)
6992 {
6993 ret = lsm6dso32_ln_pg_write_byte(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PEDO_CMD_REG,
6994 (uint8_t *)&pedo_cmd_reg);
6995 }
6996
6997 return ret;
6998}
6999
7008int32_t lsm6dso32_pedo_sens_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
7009 lsm6dso32_pedo_md_t *val)
7010{
7011 lsm6dso32_emb_func_en_a_t emb_func_en_a;
7012 lsm6dso32_emb_func_en_b_t emb_func_en_b;
7013 lsm6dso32_pedo_cmd_reg_t pedo_cmd_reg;
7014 int32_t ret;
7015
7016 ret = lsm6dso32_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSO32_PEDO_CMD_REG,
7017 (uint8_t *)&pedo_cmd_reg);
7018
7019 if (ret == 0)
7020 {
7021 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
7022 }
7023
7024 if (ret == 0)
7025 {
7026 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMB_FUNC_EN_A,
7027 (uint8_t *)&emb_func_en_a, 1);
7028 }
7029
7030 if (ret == 0)
7031 {
7032 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMB_FUNC_EN_B,
7033 (uint8_t *)&emb_func_en_b, 1);
7034 }
7035
7036 if (ret == 0)
7037 {
7038 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_USER_BANK);
7039 }
7040
7041 switch ((pedo_cmd_reg.ad_det_en << 5) | (pedo_cmd_reg.fp_rejection_en
7042 << 4) |
7043 (emb_func_en_b.pedo_adv_en << 1) | emb_func_en_a.pedo_en)
7044 {
7045 case LSM6DSO32_PEDO_DISABLE:
7046 *val = LSM6DSO32_PEDO_DISABLE;
7047 break;
7048
7049 case LSM6DSO32_PEDO_BASE_MODE:
7050 *val = LSM6DSO32_PEDO_BASE_MODE;
7051 break;
7052
7053 case LSM6DSO32_PEDO_ADV_MODE:
7054 *val = LSM6DSO32_PEDO_ADV_MODE;
7055 break;
7056
7057 case LSM6DSO32_FALSE_STEP_REJ:
7058 *val = LSM6DSO32_FALSE_STEP_REJ;
7059 break;
7060
7061 case LSM6DSO32_FALSE_STEP_REJ_ADV_MODE:
7062 *val = LSM6DSO32_FALSE_STEP_REJ_ADV_MODE;
7063 break;
7064
7065 default:
7066 *val = LSM6DSO32_PEDO_DISABLE;
7067 break;
7068 }
7069
7070 return ret;
7071}

7676int32_t lsm6dso32_mag_soft_iron_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx, int16_t *val)
7677{
7678 uint8_t buff[12];
7679 int32_t ret;
7680
7681 uint8_t index;
7682 buff[1] = (uint8_t)((uint16_t)val[0] / 256U);
7683 buff[0] = (uint8_t)((uint16_t)val[0] - (buff[1] * 256U));
7684 buff[3] = (uint8_t)((uint16_t)val[1] / 256U);
7685 buff[2] = (uint8_t)((uint16_t)val[1] - (buff[3] * 256U));
7686 buff[5] = (uint8_t)((uint16_t)val[2] / 256U);
7687 buff[4] = (uint8_t)((uint16_t)val[2] - (buff[5] * 256U));
7688 buff[7] = (uint8_t)((uint16_t)val[3] / 256U);
7689 buff[6] = (uint8_t)((uint16_t)val[3] - (buff[7] * 256U));

7702 &buff[index]);
7703 }
7704

8274int32_t lsm6dso32_fsm_enable_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
8275 lsm6dso32_emb_fsm_enable_t *val)
8276{
8277 int32_t ret;
8278
8279 lsm6dso32_emb_func_en_b_t reg;
8280 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
8281
8282 if (ret == 0)
8283 {
8284 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FSM_ENABLE_A,
8285 (uint8_t *)&val->fsm_enable_a, 1);
8286 }
8287
8288 if (ret == 0)
8289 {
8290 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FSM_ENABLE_B,
8291 (uint8_t *)&val->fsm_enable_b, 1);
8292 }
8293
8294 if (ret == 0)
8295 {
8296 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMB_FUNC_EN_B,
8297 (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
8298 }
8299
8300 if (ret == 0)
8301 {
8302 if ((val->fsm_enable_a.fsm1_en |
8303 val->fsm_enable_a.fsm2_en |
8304 val->fsm_enable_a.fsm3_en |
8305 val->fsm_enable_a.fsm4_en |
8306 val->fsm_enable_a.fsm5_en |
8307 val->fsm_enable_a.fsm6_en |
8308 val->fsm_enable_a.fsm7_en |
8309 val->fsm_enable_a.fsm8_en |
8310 val->fsm_enable_b.fsm9_en |
8311 val->fsm_enable_b.fsm10_en |
8312 val->fsm_enable_b.fsm11_en |
8313 val->fsm_enable_b.fsm12_en |
8314 val->fsm_enable_b.fsm13_en |
8315 val->fsm_enable_b.fsm14_en |
8316 val->fsm_enable_b.fsm15_en |
8317 val->fsm_enable_b.fsm16_en)
8318 != PROPERTY_DISABLE)
8319 {
8320 reg.fsm_en = PROPERTY_ENABLE;
8321 }
8322
8323 else
8324 {
8325 reg.fsm_en = PROPERTY_DISABLE;
8326 }
8327
8328 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMB_FUNC_EN_B,
8329 (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
8330 }
8331
8332 if (ret == 0)
8333 {
8334 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_USER_BANK);
8335 }
8336
8337 return ret;
8338}

8468
8478int32_t lsm6dso32_long_clr_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
8479 lsm6dso32_fsm_lc_clr_t *val)
8480{
8481 lsm6dso32_fsm_long_counter_clear_t reg;
8482 int32_t ret;
8483
8484 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
8485
8486 if (ret == 0)
8487 {
8488 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FSM_LONG_COUNTER_CLEAR,
8489 (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
8490 }
8491
8492 if (ret == 0)
8493 {
8494 switch (reg.fsm_lc_clr)
8495 {
8496 case LSM6DSO32_LC_NORMAL:
8497 *val = LSM6DSO32_LC_NORMAL;
8498 break;
8499
8500 case LSM6DSO32_LC_CLEAR:
8501 *val = LSM6DSO32_LC_CLEAR;
8502 break;
8503
8504 case LSM6DSO32_LC_CLEAR_DONE:
8505 *val = LSM6DSO32_LC_CLEAR_DONE;
8506 break;
8507
8508 default:
8509 *val = LSM6DSO32_LC_NORMAL;
8510 break;
8511 }
8512 }
8513
8514 if (ret == 0)
8515 {
8516 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_USER_BANK);
8517 }
8518
8519 return ret;
8520}

8720int32_t lsm6dso32_long_cnt_int_value_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
8721 uint16_t val)
8722{
8723 uint8_t buff[2];
8724 int32_t ret;
8725
8726 buff[1] = (uint8_t)(val / 256U);
8727 buff[0] = (uint8_t)(val - (buff[1] * 256U));
8728 ret = lsm6dso32_ln_pg_write_byte(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FSM_LC_TIMEOUT_L,
8729 &buff[0]);
8730
8731 if (ret == 0)
8732 {
8733 ret = lsm6dso32_ln_pg_write_byte(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FSM_LC_TIMEOUT_H,
8734 &buff[1]);
8735 }
8736
8737 return ret;
8738}
8739
8751int32_t lsm6dso32_long_cnt_int_value_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
8752 uint16_t *val)
8753{
8754 uint8_t buff[2];
8755 int32_t ret;
8756
8757 ret = lsm6dso32_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FSM_LC_TIMEOUT_L,
8758 &buff[0]);
8759
8760 if (ret == 0)
8761 {
8762 ret = lsm6dso32_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FSM_LC_TIMEOUT_H,
8763 &buff[1]);
8764 *val = buff[1];
8765 *val = (*val * 256U) + buff[0];
8766 }
8767
8768 return ret;
8769}

8816int32_t lsm6dso32_fsm_start_address_set(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
8817 uint16_t val)
8818{
8819 uint8_t buff[2];
8820 int32_t ret;
8821
8822 buff[1] = (uint8_t)(val / 256U);
8823 buff[0] = (uint8_t)(val - (buff[1] * 256U));
8824 ret = lsm6dso32_ln_pg_write_byte(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FSM_START_ADD_L,
8825 &buff[0]);
8826
8827 if (ret == 0)
8828 {
8829 ;
8830 ret = lsm6dso32_ln_pg_write_byte(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FSM_START_ADD_H,
8831 &buff[1]);
8832 }
8833
8834 return ret;
8835}

8846int32_t lsm6dso32_fsm_start_address_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
8847 uint16_t *val)
8848{
8849 uint8_t buff[2];
8850 int32_t ret;

8852 ret = lsm6dso32_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FSM_START_ADD_L,
8853 &buff[0]);

8855 if (ret == 0)
8856 {
8857 ret = lsm6dso32_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSO32_FSM_START_ADD_H,
8858 &buff[1]);
8859 *val = buff[1];
8860 *val = (*val * 256U) + buff[0];
8861 }
8862
8863 return ret;
8864}

9487
9496int32_t lsm6dso32_sh_data_rate_get(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
9497 lsm6dso32_shub_odr_t *val)
9498{
9499 lsm6dso32_slv0_config_t reg;
9500 int32_t ret;
9501
9502 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_SENSOR_HUB_BANK);
9503
9504 if (ret == 0)
9505 {
9506 ret = lsm6dso32_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_SLV0_CONFIG, (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
9507 }
9508
9509 if (ret == 0)
9510 {
9511 switch (reg.shub_odr)
9512 {
9513 case LSM6DSO32_SH_ODR_104Hz:
9514 *val = LSM6DSO32_SH_ODR_104Hz;
9515 break;
9516
9517 case LSM6DSO32_SH_ODR_52Hz:
9518 *val = LSM6DSO32_SH_ODR_52Hz;
9519 break;
9520
9521 case LSM6DSO32_SH_ODR_26Hz:
9522 *val = LSM6DSO32_SH_ODR_26Hz;
9523 break;
9524
9525 case LSM6DSO32_SH_ODR_13Hz:
9526 *val = LSM6DSO32_SH_ODR_13Hz;
9527 break;
9528
9529 default:
9530 *val = LSM6DSO32_SH_ODR_104Hz;
9531 break;
9532 }
9533
9534 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_USER_BANK);
9535 }
9536
9537 return ret;
9538}
9539
9551int32_t lsm6dso32_sh_cfg_write(stmdev_ctx_t *ctx,
9552 lsm6dso32_sh_cfg_write_t *val)
9553{
9554 lsm6dso32_slv0_add_t reg;
9555 int32_t ret;
9556
9557 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_SENSOR_HUB_BANK);
9558
9559 if (ret == 0)
9560 {
9561 reg.slave0 = val->slv0_add;
9562 reg.rw_0 = 0;
9563 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_SLV0_ADD, (uint8_t *)&reg, 1);
9564 }
9565
9566 if (ret == 0)
9567 {
9568 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_SLV0_SUBADD,
9569 &(val->slv0_subadd), 1);
9570 }
9571
9572 if (ret == 0)
9573 {
9574 ret = lsm6dso32_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSO32_DATAWRITE_SLV0,
9575 &(val->slv0_data), 1);
9576 }
9577
9578 if (ret == 0)
9579 {
9580 ret = lsm6dso32_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSO32_USER_BANK);
9581 }
9582
9583 return ret;
9584}
